data.description: You will love the views from this lovely 1870 sq ft home w/ 3 bedrooms & 3 baths (one full bath, two with shower & no tub). You could have a two-room guest quarters with separate entrance. Features include a living room; den or dining area; eat-in kitchen w/ gas range, microwave, dishwasher, refrigerator, oak cabinets, built-in desk, & pantry; primary bedroom w/ walk-in closet; inside laundry room w/ sink; & solar hot water heater. There is an extra refigerator, too. You will also enjoy having RV parking, an oversized extended-length two-car garage w/ workbench, shelving & sink; easy care landscaping; & covered back patio. Don't forget to check out the views!
